Diamond Shield:
	Defaults:
		Durability: 1050
		Reparable: Diamond
		Effects:
			While Idle:
				Regeneration 1
			While Using (Non-Stacking):
				Regeneration 1
			While Using and Sneaking (Non-Stacking):
				Regeneration 1
		Crafting Recipe:
			OIO
			DDD
			OIO
